
     ___________________________________________________________________________________________________
	| Method                | Interface/Class | Return Value | Best Use Case                            |
	| --------------------- | --------------- | ------------ | ---------------------------------------- |
	| `extends Thread`      | Class           | No           | Simple single thread                     |
	| `implements Runnable` | Interface       | No           | When class already extends another class |
	| Anonymous Runnable    | Interface       | No           | One-time use                             |
	| Lambda Runnable       | Interface       | No           | Clean syntax (Java 8+)                   |
	| `ExecutorService`     | Interface       | No           | Thread pooling                           |
	| `Callable` & `Future` | Interface       | Yes          | When return result needed                |
    -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    
    